    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lead your own professional esports team: sign players, play drafts, secure sponsors, and battle through full seasons in this stat-driven sim.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from over a dozen real teams.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026430/extras/37ed80ab1fd1ec35bcbf301d65c62eaf.poster.avif?t=1765812418\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026430/extras/37ed80ab1fd1ec35bcbf301d65c62eaf.webm?t=1765812418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026430/extras/37ed80ab1fd1ec35bcbf301d65c62eaf.mp4?t=1765812418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play through drafts in the game <i>within</i> the game, <strong>Aurebella</strong>, and dominate with over 80 different champs to choose from.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026430/extras/e0c29c9f412f090eb071a8a3ad6551ce.poster.avif?t=1765812418\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026430/extras/e0c29c9f412f090eb071a8a3ad6551ce.webm?t=1765812418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026430/extras/e0c29c9f412f090eb071a8a3ad6551ce.mp4?t=1765812418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick what roles each champ should fill,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026430/extras/9cec389ba93aea19adcebdecd8b7e1ba.poster.avif?t=1765812418\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026430/extras/9cec389ba93aea19adcebdecd8b7e1ba.webm?t=1765812418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026430/extras/9cec389ba93aea19adcebdecd8b7e1ba.mp4?t=1765812418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >make strategic decisions about your players, champs, and composition,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026430/extras/9aea7188909f7d894a0c581dc01302a6.poster.avif?t=1765812418\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026430/extras/9aea7188909f7d894a0c581dc01302a6.webm?t=1765812418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026430/extras/9aea7188909f7d894a0c581dc01302a6.mp4?t=1765812418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and guide your team to victory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026430/extras/ccf5fee4396d585fee13585bdcad7de7.poster.avif?t=1765812418\" width=1138 height=640 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026430/extras/ccf5fee4396d585fee13585bdcad7de7.webm?t=1765812418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026430/extras/ccf5fee4396d585fee13585bdcad7de7.mp4?t=1765812418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additional features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fill out your staff with a head coach, assistant coach, content creator, analyst, and manager</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Secure sponsorships to bankroll your squad</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage injuries, suspensions, and meta changes </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play through regular season, postseason, and international splits twice per year</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Answer questions from media members throughout the season</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And much more!</p>",
